metadata.name: The Journey Back to Hell
metadata.description:
Story :
Mr Satan is smilingly flying through the valley of death, he is piloting a restored wreck of a world war aircraft. he is going back to hell, he wants to pick up the things left there. 

Mr Satan is a retired satan, he feels useless because he sees that humans already have their own will to sin. so what is he working for? "the world will destroy itself, the real horror is in humans" he said âœ¨

About:
"The Journey Back to Hell" is Mr Satan's genesis work in the "Mr Satan's Odyssey" collection. in mp4 format, Mr Satan uses 2D retro animation as his method of creation. with a touch of sound that adds a thick feel. and in this collection, Mr Satan wants to share with you what he did during his retirement and even he will also share his experiences before his retirement.
